Version Control System : Version control is the system that records or manages the changes that are made to codes, documents programs.
It helps to track changes when multiple people work on the same project.
And Git is the version control system.

How to initialize the git ????

git init, git add, git commit -m "message"

for example,
 mkdir mouni( create a directory)
cd mouni
git init (initializing the git in the directory to track chnages)
touch file.txt (create the file)
git add file.txt (git add to the staging area)
git commit -m "file added" ( finally the file inti the git repository)




 
   
